p: In the Supplementary Material, S3 Table shows the summary of positive selection analysis performed on different datasets. M1a vs M2a test and M7 vs M8 test indicated consistently that there was no positive selection across overall DENV 4-I, Clade I, II, IV and V datasets. In Clade III dataset, no positive selection was indicated by M1a vs M2a test, however, M7 vs M8 test inferred a weak positive selection (5.6% of codons with Ï‰ = 1.193) with amino acid site 95 Pp > 0.95.
